  "title": "Videographer / Photographer / Content Creator",
  "description": "<h2>🎥 JOIN OUR TEAM</h2><p><strong>Videographer / Photographer / Content Creator</strong></p><p><strong>Brands:</strong> F&B & Lifestyle (Japanese Restaurants + Salon)<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Hybrid (WFH / Town)<br /><strong>Schedule:</strong> 5 days a week<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> Competitive package (based on experience)</p><h3>🌟 Why Join Us</h3><ul><li><p>AWS GUARANTEED</p></li><li><p>Performance bonus</p></li><li><p>Staff discounts across all our F&B and salon brands</p></li><li><p>Work across multiple established lifestyle brands</p></li><li><p>High creative exposure with room to grow</p></li></ul><h3>🎬 About the Role</h3><p>You’ll be creating short-form and visual content across our restaurant and salon brands from food and ambience to people, transformations, and lifestyle moments. This role suits someone who enjoys variety, takes ownership, and can adapt their creative eye across different brand environments.</p><h3>📌 Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Plan, shoot, and edit short-form videos for social media (INSTAGRAM & TIKTOK)</p></li><li><p>Create content showcasing food, ambience, people, and brand experiences</p></li><li><p>Edit videos with music, text, and effects optimised for platforms like Instagram and TikTok</p></li><li><p>Cover events, promotions, and behind-the-scenes moments</p></li><li><p>Ensure visual consistency across all brands</p></li><li><p>Basic graphic design support (e.g. social posts, menus, marketing visuals using Canva or Adobe tools)</p></li><li><p>Light admin coordination such as file organisation and content scheduling</p></li><li><p>Manage content timelines and deliver independently</p></li></ul><h3>🎯 What We’re Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in videography, photography, or content creation</p></li><li><p>Comfortable shooting both food and people / lifestyle content</p></li><li><p>Strong editing skills (Adobe Premiere Pro, Final Cut Pro, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Familiar with short-form content and social media trends</p></li><li><p>Self-driven, organised, and able to manage multiple brands</p></li><li><p>Open to occasional evenings or weekends for shoots</p></li></ul><h3>📲 How to Apply</h3><p>WhatsApp your <strong>resume, expected salary</strong> to <strong>+65 8868 8831</strong><br /><strong>Singaporeans only.</strong><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
